Dataviz of my full digital footprint on Facebook between 1234644109 and 1558382965, in contrast to the classification by indexed labels from the original dataset. Objects of desire explores the boundaries between mind and body, those parts among what it is inside and what it is outside that, due to its excessive naturalness, have been pushed into the backgrounds of reject and oblivion. Through the use of detached human materials, such as hair and nails, I reflect on the Freudian concept of the "uncanny" in order to remind us of our own materiality. Madrid, 2015. #objectsofdesire #uncanny #jeweldesign #speculativedesign #art #gold #hair #nails #embroidery
